## Legal Disclaimer

This project contains legal documents sourced from the official website of the 
Mexican Chamber of Deputies (Cámara de Diputados de México). These documents are 
public domain legal texts of the Mexican federal government.

The original legal documents remain the property of the Mexican government and 
are subject to their terms of use. This project provides tools and infrastructure 
for accessing, converting, and analyzing these public legal documents.

Users should verify the accuracy and currency of legal information with official 
sources before making any legal decisions based on this data.

## Data Attribution

Legal documents in this repository are sourced from:
- **Source**: Cámara de Diputados de México
- **Website**: https://www.diputados.gob.mx/LeyesBiblio/
- **License**: Public Domain (Mexican Federal Government)
- **Last Updated**: January 2024

## Third-Party Tools

This project uses various open-source tools and libraries:
- **LibreOffice**: Document conversion (Mozilla Public License)
- **Pandoc**: Document processing (GPL v2+)
- **curl**: Data download (MIT-style license)
- **bash**: Scripting environment (GPL v3+)

Please refer to individual tool licenses for their specific terms.
